Unitron/Firestarter/Vehement:



Unitron's radar picked up the incoming bots and he transformed to space 
fighter mode, launching into the air, all the shots not even touching him.

"Blasted fools!" he yelled, powering his boosters to full speed.

---

Firestarter sighed as he saw Unitron transformer and did a flip several feet 
backwards, in midair transformed to his space fighter mode, launching into 
the air.  

"Regroup closer to other robots of the faction you're in.  We won't be denied 
our destiny." he said via inner monologue comm. transmission with Unitron.

"Acknowledged." Unitron replied in in the same fashion.

---

Vehement watched Firestarter and Unitron get teamed up on by numerous 
Maximals.  "Heh heh." he laughed (similar to Christopher Lambert's laugh), 
raising his left arm, launching off an energy-signature seeking missile at 
Hot Rod.  He raised his other arm, firing a missile of the same type at Angel 
Prime.

"Let the heathens die." he muttered to himself, his crimson optics glowing 
with a strange ferocity.
